  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  
  <div class="container hero-content">
    <div class="badge animate-fade-in">
      <span>ðŸš€ Premium Web Design for Trades</span>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="animate-fade-in delay-1">
      Turn Your Hands<br>
      Into <span class="highlight-text">High-Paying Work</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="animate-fade-in delay-2">
      We build slick, high-converting websites for Plumbers, Electricians, and Builders. 
      Stop chasing leads. Let them come to you.
    </p>
    
    <div class="cta-group animate-fade-in delay-3">
